<br>
I just wonder why we are so quick to impose this standard on politicians, yet not so much for the others mentioned.<br>
<br>
Don't get me wrong here, I still think infidelity is abhorrent, but I'm not sure that it is grounds for someone needing to leave their job (other than clergy, who are required to practice what they preach).<br>
